summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to annexation, land use and zoning; annexing to The City of Seattle portions of Section 32, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and Sections 5 and 6, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M., in King County; adding new Plats 302 E and 303 W to the Official Land Use Map and Amending Plat 78 W, Page 183 thereof to zone the annexed property in the Commercial 2 Zone (C2/65'), and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith.
